# ğŸ“Š Scientific Calculator API (FastAPI)

A secure, modular, full-featured API built using **FastAPI**. This project performs advanced mathematical operations, handles authentication, logs operations to a **MySQL** database, streams audio files, and supports asynchronous background tasks â€” all in one API.

